1233
01:13:35,745 --> 01:13:39,396
MEREDITH: I-I told that man
that I only want to visit you.

1234
01:13:39,416 --> 01:13:41,474
That I want to stay here.

1235
01:13:41,567 --> 01:13:43,809
That's what daddy
