01:22:30,446 --> 01:22:31,186
AIRLINE EMPLOYEE:
Morning...

1335
01:22:31,338 --> 01:22:32,780
LIZBETH: Hi.

1336
01:22:32,931 --> 01:22:39,102
[dramatic music]

1337
01:22:39,121 --> 01:22:41,104
AIRLINE EMPLOYEE: Thank you.
