01:23:16,492 --> 01:23:17,549
CUSTOM'S OFFICIAL:
Kalimera.

1342
01:23:17,568 --> 01:23:18,784
LIZBETH:
Good morning.

1343
01:23:19,495 --> 01:23:27,495
[tense music]

1344
01:23:34,343 --> 01:23:35,676
[tense music]

1345
01:23:35,827 --> 01:23:36,752
CUSTOM'S OFFICIAL:
Have a good flight.

1346
01:23:36,904 --> 01:23:37,761
LIZBETH:
Thank you.

